<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>QuantAI Studio | Professional Algorithmic Backtesting by StackX Lab</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.js"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: 'class',
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    fontFamily: { sans: ['"Plus Jakarta Sans"', 'sans-serif'] },
                    colors: {
                        brand: { 50: '#f0fdfa', 100: '#ccfbf1', 400: '#2dd4bf', 500: '#14b8a6', 600: '#0d9488', 900: '#134e4a', 950: '#042f2e' },
                        stackx: { start: '#3B82F6', end: '#8B5CF6' },
                        surface: { dark: '#0A0A0B', darkBorder: '#1F1F22' }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; }
        .glass-panel { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); }
        .text-gradient { background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, #a1a1aa); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        .stackx-gradient { background: linear-gradient(to right, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        .glow-bg { position: absolute; width: 600px; height: 600px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(20,184,166,0.15) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 70%); top: -200px; left: -100px; z-index: -1; pointer-events: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-surface-dark text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50 antialiased selection:bg-brand-500 selection:text-white transition-colors duration-300">

    <div class="glow-bg hidden dark:block"></div>

    <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 transition-all duration-300 border-b border-transparent dark:border-white/5 bg-white/70 dark:bg-surface-dark/70 backdrop-blur-md">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center h-20">
                
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 cursor-pointer">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-brand-500 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/30">
                        <i class="fas fa-layer-group text-white text-sm"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
                        <span class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-none">QuantAI</span>
                        <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-0.5 tracking-wide">
                            BY STACK<span class="stackx-gradient font-extrabold">X</span> LAB
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-8">
                    <a href="#features" class="smooth-scroll text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-brand-500 dark:hover:text-white transition-colors">Features</a>
                    <a href="#pricing" class="smooth-scroll text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-brand-500 dark:hover:text-white transition-colors">Pricing</a>
                    <a href="#faq" class="smooth-scroll text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-brand-500 dark:hover:text-white transition-colors">FAQ</a>
                    <a href="#contact" class="smooth-scroll text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-brand-500 dark:hover:text-white transition-colors">Contact</a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                    <button id="themeToggle" class="p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-slate-200 dark:hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
                        <i class="fas fa-moon dark:hidden"></i>
                        <i class="fas fa-sun hidden dark:block"></i>
                    </button>
                    <% if (typeof isLoggedIn !== 'undefined' && isLoggedIn) { %>
                        <a href="/dashboard" class="bg-slate-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-black px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-slate-800 dark:hover:bg-slate-200 transition-all shadow-md">Dashboard</a>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <a href="/auth/login" class="hidden md:block text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 hover:text-brand-500 dark:hover:text-white transition-colors">Log in</a>
                        <a href="/auth/signup" class="bg-slate-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-black px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-slate-800 dark:hover:bg-slate-200 transition-all shadow-md">Get Started</a>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="relative pt-40 pb-20 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000">
                
                <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 bg-white dark:bg-[#111113] border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/10 rounded-full px-5 py-2 mb-8 hover:border-blue-500/50 dark:hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all shadow-sm cursor-pointer group">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M4 4L20 20M20 4L4 20" stroke="url(#paint0_linear_hero)" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        <path d="M4 10L14 20M20 14L10 4" stroke="url(#paint1_linear_hero)" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" opacity="0.5"/>
                        <defs>
                            <linearGradient id="paint0_linear_hero" x1="4" y1="4" x2="20" y2="20" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                                <stop stop-color="#3B82F6"/>
                                <stop offset="1" stop-color="#8B5CF6"/>
                            </linearGradient>
                            <linearGradient id="paint1_linear_hero" x1="4" y1="10" x2="20" y2="14" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                                <stop stop-color="#3B82F6"/>
                                <stop offset="1" stop-color="#8B5CF6"/>
                            </linearGradient>
                        </defs>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 tracking-wide">
                        A flagship product developed by <span class="stackx-gradient font-bold">StackX Lab</span> &rarr;
                    </span>
                </a>

                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight dark:text-white text-slate-900">
                    Institutional Backtesting, <br/><span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-500 to-emerald-400">Powered by AI.</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-10 max-w-2xl">
                    Deploy, test, and optimize complex trading logic in natural language. Access high-fidelity market data instantly without writing a single line of boilerplate Python.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 w-full sm:w-auto">
                    <% if (typeof isLoggedIn !== 'undefined' && isLoggedIn) { %>
                        <a href="/dashboard" class="bg-brand-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-brand-600 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/25 flex items-center justify-center group">
                            Go to Dashboard
                            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
                        </a>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <a href="/auth/signup" class="bg-brand-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-brand-600 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/25 flex items-center justify-center group">
                            Start Building
                            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
                        </a>
                    <% } %>
                    <a href="#contact" class="smooth-scroll px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold border border-slate-300 dark:border-surface-darkBorder text-slate-700 dark:text-white hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-all flex items-center justify-center">
                        Contact Sales
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-20 relative mx-auto max-w-5xl" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" data-aos-duration="1200">
                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/10 bg-white dark:bg-[#111113] shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="h-12 border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 flex items-center px-4 space-x-2 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#0A0A0B]">
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-400"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-400"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 md:p-10 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                        <div class="md:col-span-1 space-y-4">
                            <div class="h-4 w-24 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-white/10 rounded"></div>
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <div class="h-3 w-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-white/5 rounded"></div>
                                <div class="h-3 w-4/5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-white/5 rounded"></div>
                                <div class="h-3 w-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-white/5 rounded"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5">
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                                    <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Sharpe Ratio</span>
                                    <span class="text-sm font-bold text-brand-500">2.14</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                                    <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Win Rate</span>
                                    <span class="text-sm font-bold dark:text-white">64.2%</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="md:col-span-2 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#0A0A0B] p-4 flex items-end space-x-2 h-48">
                            <div class="w-full bg-brand-500/20 dark:bg-brand-500/40 rounded-t" style="height: 30%"></div>
                            <div class="w-full bg-brand-500/40 dark:bg-brand-500/60 rounded-t" style="height: 50%"></div>
                            <div class="w-full bg-red-400/40 dark:bg-red-500/60 rounded-t" style="height: 20%"></div>
                            <div class="w-full bg-brand-500/60 dark:bg-brand-500/80 rounded-t" style="height: 65%"></div>
                            <div class="w-full bg-brand-500 rounded-t" style="height: 90%"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features" class="py-24 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-surface-dark border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight">Precision tools for modern markets.</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">No code, no infrastructure setup. Just raw computational power directed by your logic.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="md:col-span-2 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder bg-white dark:bg-[#111113] hover:border-brand-500/50 transition-colors shadow-sm" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-brand-50 dark:bg-brand-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <i class="fas fa-brain text-brand-500"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Natural Language Engine</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-6 max-w-md">Describe your entry and exit conditions in plain English. Our LLM compiles it directly into highly optimized Python vector operations under the hood.</p>
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#0A0A0B] border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 font-mono text-sm text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-300">
                        > "Buy when 50 EMA crosses over 200 EMA on the 1H timeframe, set stop loss at 1 ATR."
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder bg-white dark:bg-[#111113] hover:border-brand-500/50 transition-colors shadow-sm" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <i class="fas fa-database text-blue-500"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Tick-Level Data</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Access up to 10 years of historical data across Crypto, Forex, and Equities. No API keys needed.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder bg-white dark:bg-[#111113] hover:border-brand-500/50 transition-colors shadow-sm" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <i class="fas fa-wand-magic-sparkles text-purple-500"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Auto-Optimization</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Identify peak parameter settings with automated Walk-Forward Analysis and Monte Carlo simulations.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="md:col-span-2 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder bg-white dark:bg-[#111113] hover:border-brand-500/50 transition-colors shadow-sm" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-pie text-green-500"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Institutional Tear Sheets</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-6">Export PDF reports featuring Sharpe, Sortino, Max Drawdown, Profit Factor, and CAGR to present to investors or track your own edge.</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/10 text-xs font-semibold">Sharpe Ratio</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/10 text-xs font-semibold">Calmar Ratio</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/10 text-xs font-semibold">Max Drawdown</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="pricing" class="py-24 bg-white dark:bg-[#0A0A0B] border-y border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 relative">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight">Pay for execution, not subscriptions.</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Credit-based pricing means you only pay when you successfully run a backtest. No hidden fees.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#111113] shadow-xl" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse min-w-[700px]">
                    <thead>
                        <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">
                            <th class="p-6 w-1/3">
                                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Compare Plans</span>
                            </th>
                            <th class="p-6 w-1/3 bg-white dark:bg-[#161618] border-x border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">
                                <div class="text-lg font-bold mb-1">QUICK Backtest</div>
                                <div class="text-brand-500 font-semibold mb-3">3 Credits</div>
                                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-normal mb-4">Fast validation & idea testing.</p>
                                <button class="w-full py-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-300 dark:border-white/20 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">Select Quick</button>
                            </th>
                            <th class="p-6 w-1/3 relative border-r border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">
                                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-brand-500"></div>
                                <div class="text-lg font-bold mb-1">DEEP Backtest</div>
                                <div class="text-brand-500 font-semibold mb-3">12 Credits</div>
                                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-normal mb-4">Institutional grade research & optimization.</p>
                                <button class="w-full py-2 rounded-lg bg-brand-500 text-white text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-brand-600 transition-colors">Select Deep</button>
                            </th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody class="text-sm">
                        <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">
                            <td class="p-4 pl-6 font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Input Limit</td>
                            <td class="p-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#161618] border-x border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">150 words</td>
                            <td class="p-4 border-r border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">1,500 words</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">
                            <td class="p-4 pl-6 font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Assets</td>
                            <td class="p-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#161618] border-x border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">Up to 2</td>
                            <td class="p-4 border-r border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">Unlimited</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">
                            <td class="p-4 pl-6 font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Complexity</td>
                            <td class="p-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#161618] border-x border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">Up to 3 indicators</td>
                            <td class="p-4 border-r border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">Unlimited indicators & logic</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">
                            <td class="p-4 pl-6 font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Timeframes Available</td>
                            <td class="p-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#161618] border-x border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">1h, 1d</td>
                            <td class="p-4 border-r border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">1m, 5m, 15m, 30m, 1h, 4h, 1d</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">
                            <td class="p-4 pl-6 font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Data History Limits</td>
                            <td class="p-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#161618] border-x border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">Max 1 year</td>
                            <td class="p-4 border-r border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder text-xs space-y-1 text-slate-500">
                                <div>1m: 7-15d | 5m: 90-180d | 15m: 1-2y</div>
                                <div>30m: 2-3y | 1h: 5y | 4h: 8y | 1d: Max</div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">
                            <td class="p-4 pl-6 font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Advanced Features</td>
                            <td class="p-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#161618] border-x border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder text-slate-400">None</td>
                            <td class="p-4 border-r border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder font-semibold text-brand-500">Walk-Forward & Monte Carlo (+3 cr Opt.)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">
                            <td class="p-4 pl-6 font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Model</td>
                            <td class="p-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#161618] border-x border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">Flash</td>
                            <td class="p-4 border-r border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder text-brand-500">Pro</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="p-4 pl-6 font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Execution Speed</td>
                            <td class="p-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#161618] border-x border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder text-brand-500 font-bold">~30 sec</td>
                            <td class="p-4 border-r border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder">2-5 min</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="faq" class="py-24 border-y border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-surface-dark">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-10 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-[#111113] overflow-hidden">
                    <button class="faq-btn w-full px-6 py-4 text-left font-semibold flex justify-between items-center focus:outline-none hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
                        How does the credit system work?
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down transition-transform duration-300 text-brand-500"></i>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mt-2 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 pt-4">
                        You purchase credits in bulk. A standard run costs 1 credit. If your natural language prompt results in an error due to logic flaws, our system attempts an auto-fix. If it completely fails to generate a backtest, zero credits are deducted. You only pay for successful outputs.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-[#111113] overflow-hidden">
                    <button class="faq-btn w-full px-6 py-4 text-left font-semibold flex justify-between items-center focus:outline-none hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
                        Do I need to know how to code?
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down transition-transform duration-300 text-brand-500"></i>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mt-2 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 pt-4">
                        No. Our proprietary AI engine interprets standard trading terminology (e.g., "VWAP", "RSI divergence", "Trailing Stop") and builds the Python execution environment automatically in the background.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-surface-darkBorder rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-[#111113] overflow-hidden">
